  "small_talks": [
    {
      "id": "acha_st_tea_1",
      "text": "外公说，茶如人生，苦尽甘来。$[PLAYER_NAME]，你种的那片茶田，已经慢慢有他的影子了。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "acha_st_tea_2",
      "text": "好茶需要三个条件：好山、好水、好人工。$[PLAYER_NAME]，我们的云海山庄，三个都占了。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "acha_st_weather",
      "text": "今天的$[WEATHER]，最适合坐在观云台上看云海发呆。$[PLAYER_NAME]，你平时喜欢什么样的天气？",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "acha_st_season",
      "text": "现在是$[SEASON]了。我最喜欢这个季节的……其实，每个季节都好，都有它独特的美。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "acha_st_heart_low",
      "text": "$[PLAYER_NAME]，你还记得我们小时候在茶田里捉迷藏吗？那时候的日子真简单。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 100,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "acha_st_heart_mid",
      "text": "你离开的这些年，我每年春天都会在茶田里等你回来。今年……终于等到了。",
