      "favor_max": 400,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 2,
      "heart_max": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "acha_st_heart_high",
      "text": "$[PLAYER_NAME]，有你在的山庄，才像个家。外公说得对，云海山庄需要有人守护。",
      "favor_min": 200,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 6,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "acha_st_cloud",
      "text": "云海的状态会影响茶叶的品质。你观察过吗？大潮时采的茶，泡出来有一种特别的光泽。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
